generic:link.msg:message: The total position at the end of the month (units) reported on form T01.01 ({sum($b)}) does not correspond with the total of rows on form T07.02 ({$a}). When reporting in Excel, please check that you have correctly copied or dragged down the formatting of the first row to all subsequent rows. Rows without the correct formatting are not recognized by the XBRL-conversion tool.
